    <main>
        <section class="history">
            <h2>Our History</h2>
            <p>
                Prince Guide was born out of a passion for empowering commerce students with the knowledge and tools they need to succeed. Established as an online educational platform, it focuses on simplifying complex topics in commerce for students in higher secondary (Class 11 & 12) and B.Com levels.
            </p>
            <p>
                Since its inception, Prince Guide has gained a reputation for delivering high-quality content tailored to the NEP 2020 framework. With a mission to make learning accessible, engaging, and effective, it has become a go-to resource for students across India.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="milestones">
            <h2>Key Milestones</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>2021:</strong> Launched the first set of educational videos and notes for Class 11 and 12 commerce students.</li>
                <li><strong>2022:</strong> Expanded to cover B.Com subjects and introduced personalized tutoring through live sessions.</li>
                <li><strong>2023:</strong> Reached 10,000 subscribers on YouTube and introduced interactive quizzes and infographics.</li>
                <li><strong>2024:</strong> Released the “Commerce Series” focusing on textbook chapters and exam preparation tips.</li>
                <li><strong>2025:</strong> Hosted free workshops and webinars for commerce students nationwide.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="vision">
            <h2>Our Vision & Mission</h2>
            <p>
                At Prince Guide, our vision is to be the most trusted educational platform for commerce students. We aim to inspire and empower students to achieve academic excellence and build a strong foundation for their future careers.
            </p>
        </section>
